Package: hwtest
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Section: python
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Depends: python-dbus | python2.4-dbus, python-apt | python2.4-apt, hal, fping, xbase-clients, libxrandr2
Description: Hardware test
 This project provides an interface for gathering hardware details and
 prompting the user for questions. This information can then be sent
 to Launchpad.

